1. *Linija* je između dve tačke. (The line is between two points.)
2. *Linija* se preseče. (The line intersects.)
3. Ona se nalazi iznad *linije*. (She is located above the line.)
4. On je prešao *liniju*. (He crossed the line.)
5. Oni su napravili *liniju*. (They made the line.)
6. Ona je stavila karticu preko *linije*. (She put the card over the line.)
7. *Linija* je bila crvena. (The line was red.)
8. *Linija* je iscrtana. (The line was drawn.)